<urn:lofts:fhg.3.cornelius_alexander_polyhistor:102.1>  Judoeam Alexander Polyhistor dictam ait a liberis Semiramidis Juda et Idumaea, uti vero Claudius lolaus refert, a Judaeo Sparto, qui Thebis cum Bacchi exercitu profectus est. 
